<br>
FYI When I say farmed, im talking a group of lvl 44+ 6 man team just TRASHING thru them at break neck speeds, mobile camp, running with /stick on the main tank from spawn to spawn. <br>
<br>
In all that time, we received 3 large clay sheilds, 3 medium clay shields, 1 small shield, 2 clay axes, 1 swd, one pair of leather gaunts, one pair of leather leggings. As you can deduce, the drops were abysmal comparatively.<br>
<br>
